    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/db61c2403ecd027e95a610404e41e6b8.poster.avif?t=1770122659\" width=682 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/db61c2403ecd027e95a610404e41e6b8.webm?t=1770122659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/db61c2403ecd027e95a610404e41e6b8.mp4?t=1770122659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Description</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lighthaze World: A Serene Puzzle Adventure: Embark on a heartwarming journey with Nym and their loyal canine companion, Chewy. Start in a peaceful park, but when hunger strikes, the bustling Lighthaze World mall becomes a daunting obstacle. Nym, an anxious hero, must navigate this overwhelming space to find food for Chewy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/e447a79bdfb986d8e54db696647b9524.poster.avif?t=1770122659\" width=682 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/e447a79bdfb986d8e54db696647b9524.webm?t=1770122659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/e447a79bdfb986d8e54db696647b9524.mp4?t=1770122659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>As Nym's anxiety takes hold, their perception of the mall shifts, transforming into a serene Tasmanian wilderness. Explore lush forests, sandy beaches, towering mountains, and hidden hinterlands, all while solving puzzles and collecting items. Can you help Nym overcome their fears and find their way through this unique world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you guide Nym to success and ensure Chewy gets their much-needed meal?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/fa8d05d741ca38821984aeaffffb1392.poster.avif?t=1770122659\" width=682 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/fa8d05d741ca38821984aeaffffb1392.webm?t=1770122659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/fa8d05d741ca38821984aeaffffb1392.mp4?t=1770122659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tRelaxing Puzzle Gameplay: Enjoy a calming and accessible puzzle experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tBeautiful Tasmanian Landscapes: Immerse yourself in stunning, hand-crafted environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\t8 Levels: all the levels have many areas to explore including rooms like caves, dungeons and houses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tPuzzles order: most levels allow the player to pick and choose the puzzle order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tHeartwarming Narrative: Follow Nym's journey of overcoming anxiety and finding courage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tUnique World Exploration: Discover a world transformed by Nym's imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tNo combat: this is a puzzle and exploration game only.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tGamepad or Keyboard and mouse controls </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/6449e96d375e305b3a014dee7a87f7ec.poster.avif?t=1770122659\" width=682 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/6449e96d375e305b3a014dee7a87f7ec.webm?t=1770122659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/6449e96d375e305b3a014dee7a87f7ec.mp4?t=1770122659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for the Screen Australia support!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747190/extras/1995bceb5239bffa205aa78403b53298.webp?t=1770122659\" width=160 height=30 /></span></p>",
